        django-pesapal
        =============================
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-pesapal.png
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-pesapal
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/odero/django-pesapal.png?branch=master
